      <title>美国职位空缺数量创三个月新高，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-climb-to-three-month-high-exceeding-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国八月份职位空缺数量增至三个月来的最高水平，这一发展与其他表明工人需求放缓的数据形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-climb-to-three-month-high-exceeding-forecasts</guid>
