    <item>
      <title>前对冲基金交易员成立团体以结束政治分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ex-hedge-fund-trader-starts-group-to-tackle-political-dysfunction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金 Citadel 前全球固定收益交易主管德里克·考夫曼 (Derek Kaufman) 正在开始尝试突破美国政治的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ex-hedge-fund-trader-starts-group-to-tackle-political-dysfunction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二叠纪天然气开始通过德克萨斯州马特洪管道输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马特洪峰快线管道 (Matterhorn Express Pipeline) 已开始向 Williams Cos. 的 Transco 管道输送天然气，这是二叠纪盆地中游基础设施期待已久的补充。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰大选前公布免费预算案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰政府利用跨国公司收入飙升和苹果公司补缴税款带来的财政状况，向选民提供了免费预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:11:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚任职时间最长的央行行长获得新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-mandate-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚央行行长穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 获得议会批准，延长其五年任期，成为世界上任职时间最长的央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-mandate-in-romania</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:51:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗计划五年内每年盈利 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apollo-projects-10-billion-of-annual-earnings-in-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 预计，到 2029 年，其资产管理和退休业务的年收益将达到 100 亿美元，这得益于投资者对私人信贷和年金的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apollo-projects-10-billion-of-annual-earnings-in-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗冲突风险刺激避险需求，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫一名高级官员表示，有迹象表明伊朗正准备立即袭击以色列，这刺激了全球对避险资产的需求，美国债券价格随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有迹象显示伊朗准备袭击以色列，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明伊朗正准备对以色列发动导弹袭击，这将扩大中东冲突并可能增加原油供应中断的可能性，导致油价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券上涨，股票下跌，因中东担忧加剧：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫称有迹象表明伊朗正准备袭击以色列后，债券收益率和股票下跌，而黄金价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球债务狂潮带来创纪录的 6000 亿美元债券销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一个月，全球各地的企业和政府纷纷涌入债券市场，抓住美国总统大选前利率下降的机会，许多人担心大选将引发市场动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
